🧰 Wiring Instructions
==========================================================
🛠️ Components You'll Need
- Arduino Uno
- 4x4 Keypad
- 16x2 LCD or I2C LCD
- Jumper wires
- Breadboard
- Optional: Resistors, power supply
==========================================================
🔢 Keypad (4x4)
- Rows (R1–R4) → Arduino pins D5, D4, D3, D2
- Columns (C1–C4) → Arduino pins A3, A2, A1, A0
==========================================================
📺 LCD (16x2 in 4-bit mode)
- VSS → GND
- VDD → 5V
- V0 → GND (or middle pin of a 10k potentiometer for contrast)
- RS → D12
- RW → GND
- E → D11
- D4–D7 → D10, D9, D8, D7 respectively
===========================================================
